-- Al-Khodari Sons Wins $36 Million Contract From Health Ministry
-- B y   W a e l   M a h d i
-- 2012-01-01T09:06:34Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-01/al-khodari-sons-wins-36-million-contract-from-health-ministry.html
Abdullah A.M. Al-Khodari Sons Co. (ALKHODAR)  won
a 134.3 million riyals ($36 million) contract from the Ministry
of Health to build a 100-bed hospital in the city of Abqaiq
within 36 months, the Al Khobar-based company said in a
statement on the Saudi bourse website today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Wael Mahdi in Riyadh at 
 wmahdi@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Shaji Mathew at 
 shajimathew@bloomberg.net  